<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n53123r"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53123r">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53123r"> 123(r)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Magada</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Et le h&eacute;ros s&apos;en alla vers le pays de <mark>Magadha</mark>, et l&agrave;, seul dans la m&eacute;ditation, il demeura sur le penchant d&apos;une montagne, pr&egrave;s de la ville de <mark>R&acirc;jagriha</mark>. <small> A. Ferdinand Herold, <a name="AFHB" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#AFHB"><cite title="source">La Vie Du Bouddha</cite></a> (1922) 69f</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: Siddharta spent some months living in a cell with the sage Arata-Kalama before wandering through the lands of Magadha. </mm> </dd></dl>
